    <item>
      <title>Humans Are Exceptional</title>
      <link>https://linguage.github.io/naval/orig/humans-are-exceptional/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Oct 2021 16:56:05 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://linguage.github.io/naval/orig/humans-are-exceptional/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://linguage.github.io/naval/zh/humans-are-exceptional.zh/&#34;&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:grid-cols-2&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;div&#xA;  class=&#34;link-card group relative my-3 w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-[var(--lc-border,rgba(15,23,42,0.12))] bg-[var(--lc-bg,var(--card-bg,var(--surface,#ffffff))))] transition-shadow duration-150 hover:shadow-[var(--lc-shadow-hover,0_14px_30px_-18px_rgba(15,23,42,0.35))]&#34;&#xA;  data-url=&#34;https://nav.al/exceptional&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a&#xA;    class=&#34;link-card__fallback block px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--lc-url,var(--link-color,#0e6a85))] underline-offset-4 hover:underline&#34;&#xA;    href=&#34;https://nav.al/exceptional&#34;&#xA;    target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xA;    rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;  &gt;&#xA;    https://nav.al/exceptional&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div&#xA;  class=&#34;link-card group relative my-3 w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-[var(--lc-border,rgba(15,23,42,0.12))] bg-[var(--lc-bg,var(--card-bg,var(--surface,#ffffff))))] transition-shadow duration-150 hover:shadow-[var(--lc-shadow-hover,0_14px_30px_-18px_rgba(15,23,42,0.35))]&#34;&#xA;  data-url=&#34;https://x.com/naval/status/1002103360646823936&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a&#xA;    class=&#34;link-card__fallback block px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--lc-url,var(--link-color,#0e6a85))] underline-offset-4 hover:underline&#34;&#xA;    href=&#34;https://x.com/naval/status/1002103360646823936&#34;&#xA;    target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xA;    rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;  &gt;&#xA;    https://x.com/naval/status/1002103360646823936&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#34;humans-are-exceptional&#34;&gt;Humans Are Exceptional&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Oct 22 2021&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Humans aren&amp;rsquo;t just a form of bacteria that overran the planet&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Naval:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Three out of these four theories have an interesting pattern to them. With good explanations in epistemology, we&amp;rsquo;re saying conjectures and their refutations and error correction is how we improve knowledge. With genetic evolution, genetic mutations, variation and natural selection weed out the ones that didn&amp;rsquo;t work. Then there&amp;rsquo;s memetic evolution on top of that, where we have ideas and then criticism weeds out the ideas that don&amp;rsquo;t work.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>No Truth Can Be Justified</title>
      <link>https://linguage.github.io/naval/orig/no-truth-can-be-justified/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Oct 2021 14:48:29 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://linguage.github.io/naval/orig/no-truth-can-be-justified/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://linguage.github.io/naval/zh/no-truth-can-be-justified.zh/&#34;&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:grid-cols-2&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;div&#xA;  class=&#34;link-card group relative my-3 w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-[var(--lc-border,rgba(15,23,42,0.12))] bg-[var(--lc-bg,var(--card-bg,var(--surface,#ffffff))))] transition-shadow duration-150 hover:shadow-[var(--lc-shadow-hover,0_14px_30px_-18px_rgba(15,23,42,0.35))]&#34;&#xA;  data-url=&#34;https://nav.al/justified&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a&#xA;    class=&#34;link-card__fallback block px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--lc-url,var(--link-color,#0e6a85))] underline-offset-4 hover:underline&#34;&#xA;    href=&#34;https://nav.al/justified&#34;&#xA;    target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xA;    rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;  &gt;&#xA;    https://nav.al/justified&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div&#xA;  class=&#34;link-card group relative my-3 w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-[var(--lc-border,rgba(15,23,42,0.12))] bg-[var(--lc-bg,var(--card-bg,var(--surface,#ffffff))))] transition-shadow duration-150 hover:shadow-[var(--lc-shadow-hover,0_14px_30px_-18px_rgba(15,23,42,0.35))]&#34;&#xA;  data-url=&#34;https://x.com/naval/status/1002103360646823936&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a&#xA;    class=&#34;link-card__fallback block px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--lc-url,var(--link-color,#0e6a85))] underline-offset-4 hover:underline&#34;&#xA;    href=&#34;https://x.com/naval/status/1002103360646823936&#34;&#xA;    target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xA;    rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;  &gt;&#xA;    https://x.com/naval/status/1002103360646823936&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#34;no-truth-can-be-justified&#34;&gt;No Truth Can Be Justified&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Oct 15 2021&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&amp;lsquo;Knowledge&amp;rsquo; is just our best guess at the time&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Brett:&lt;/strong&gt;&#xA;Initial guesses at what &amp;lsquo;knowledge&amp;rsquo; was all about amounted to what is known as the &amp;ldquo;justified true belief&amp;rdquo; vision of knowledge, and it&amp;rsquo;s still the most prevalent idea today. Anyone who calls themself a &lt;strong&gt;Bayesian&lt;/strong&gt; is a justified true believer.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
